{"tid":1053994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又過了一年","createTime":"2019-03-09T13:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T12:25:07.000Z","uid":36961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0e03f32141eb6d48b3186c0e8be933a459049c","tid":1053994,"uid":36961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:38:33.000Z","msg":"每年呢個時候 都會手多執間房<br />\n明明知 執完可能都仲係咁亂<br />\n但都想做番次掃除<br />\n點知睇番啲野 先知道 哦原來時間過得咁快<br />\n小學個本紀念冊 中學同學寫既聖誕卡<br />\nOcamp啲人寫既龜背<br />\n你第一個女朋友送比你既禮物 你第一次整禮物比人整剩既既材料 傷得你最深既人 你傷得最深既人<br />\n一啲已經唔存在唔再同你人生有交集既人同埋事<br />\n雖然係咁 但係你都好唔捨得咁將佢地扔左佢<br />\n永遠都留番一個位擺呢堆野 明知呢啲野係有幾無用 你都唔會扔佢<br />\n可能直到有一日 你會扔走佢地 但唔係依一刻<br />\n因為 你仲未放低到呢啲記憶 或者係自己念舊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位reading week快樂"},{"pid":"49a5fb7e1f3293a27ee7a27c80efc476dd8f4188","tid":1053994,"uid":213463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:39:55.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"47456e1cbc119f61bacbed4f9e2b0e73c8f5feb1","tid":1053994,"uid":142872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:49:27.000Z","msg":"輝輝唔好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c13542fde7a0a5765411bd24dc09dd5b5b7a18","tid":1053994,"uid":224565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T09:33:34.000Z","msg":"reading week不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853b2c3299a1aba1aa822ed7f45c1943f85db357","tid":1053994,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T11:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5045418a57bfae689a06fb2fe7b7695cbc67cb98","tid":1053994,"uid":224565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47456e1cbc119f61bacbed4f9e2b0e73c8f5feb1","tid":1053994,"uid":142872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:49:27.000Z","msg":"輝輝唔好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"h